data.description: Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2 and a half bathrooms, 2 living areas, formal dining room, a covered porch, washer & dryer connections on second level, and a storage shed in the backyard. With more than 2300 square foot of living space, a two car garage and fenced back yard there's plenty of room for activities. On the first floor you will find the guest bedroom and connected half bath. The kitchen opens up to the breakfast nook and first floor living room. Upstairs you'll find a full bathroom and three more bedrooms along with a separate laundry room, attic access and a game room/living room. The formal dining room can easily be converted to a home office or study. The schools are Victoria Walker Elementary, E.F. Green Middle School & Goose Creek Memorial High School. Neighborhood has large lakes with two trails.
